title: Taste of Italy -premium italian recipes
description:
Enjoy fine Italian cuisine without paying hefty restaurant bills!!
We bring to you the largest collection of classical as well as Modern Italian recipes.
This is one stop Italian recipe application.This will be the best free recipe app for you.If 
you love cooking and Italian food this app will be a true companion for you!!
**Features
150+ recipes,accessible offline.
Clean,efficient and easy to use interface.
Supports user ratings.
Bookmark favorite recipes.
Highly simplified recipes for beginners.
Covers all categories of Italian cuisine like starters,main course,pizzas,pastas,and desserts.
